  45:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * @endverbatim
  46:project/src/sysmem.c ****  *
  47:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * this implementation starts allocating at the '_end' linker symbol
  48:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * the '_min_stack_size' linker symbol reserves a memory for the msp stack
  49:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * the implementation considers '_estack' linker symbol to be ram end
  50:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * note: if the msp stack, at any point during execution, grows larger than the
  51:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * reserved size, please increase the '_min_stack_size'.
  52:project/src/sysmem.c ****  *
  53:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * @param incr memory size
  54:project/src/sysmem.c ****  * @return pointer to allocated memory
